---
const stats = [
  { num: "100%", label: "Original work,\nevery time" },
  { num: "3",    label: "Core disciplines\nunder one roof" },
  { num: "∞",   label: "Revisions until\nit's right" },
  { num: "0",    label: "Templates.\nEver." },
];
---

<section id="story" class="grid grid-cols-2 min-h-screen">

  <!-- Left: text -->
  <div class="px-12 py-[120px] pr-20 border-r border-light-gray flex flex-col justify-center">
    <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-red mb-10">
      // A note from the founder
    </p>

    <h2 class="font-playfair text-[clamp(36px,4vw,60px)] font-bold leading-[1.1] text-black mb-9">
      We don't do <em class="italic text-mid-gray">average.</em><br />
      Neither do you.
    </h2>

    <div class="font-mono text-[13px] leading-[2] text-mid-gray max-w-[480px] space-y-5">
      <p>
        Most brands are invisible. Not because they're bad — but because they look like
        everyone else. They hired the cheapest option, settled for stock photos, and
        called it marketing.
      </p>
      <p>
        We built Array Studio for brands that refuse to blend in. Whether you're launching
        something new or reinventing what you've got, we bring the visual firepower to make
        your audience stop scrolling and start paying attention.
      </p>
      <p>
        We're a tight-knit crew — videographers, photographers, and a graphic designer who
        thinks in systems. We work with you like a partner, not a vendor.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10">
      <p class="font-playfair italic text-[18px] text-black">[Your Name]</p>
      <p class="font-mono text-[10px] tracking-[0.2em] uppercase text-mid-gray mt-1">
        Founder, Array Studio
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Right: stats on black -->
  <div class="bg-black flex flex-col justify-center items-center px-20 py-20 relative overflow-hidden">
    <!-- BG word -->
    <div class="absolute font-bebas text-[clamp(80px,12vw,180px)] text-white/[0.05] leading-none pointer-events-none select-none">
      ARRAY
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-[2px] w-full relative z-10">
      {
        stats.map((stat) => (
          <div class="reveal bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/[0.06] px-9 py-12 hover:bg-gold/[0.08] transition-colors duration-200">
            <div class="font-playfair text-[56px] font-black text-gold leading-none mb-2">
              {stat.num}
            </div>
            <div class="font-mono text-[11px] tracking-[0.15em] uppercase text-cream/45 whitespace-pre-line">
              {stat.label}
            </div>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
